Condensor? Tach? Sometimes internal short in the
points assembly. Sometimes the wires inside the
distributor that have to flex as the base plate
rotates (advance) sometimes those wires work harden
and the insulation fails - usually very intermittant
though. Did you bring an extra coil with you?:o)
